      • SolarSystemModel

        public SolarSystemModel()
        Initializes a new instance of the SolarSystemModel class. Reads data from the JSON document and creates models.

      • SolarSystemModel

        public SolarSystemModel​(java.lang.String resource)
        Initializes a new instance of the SolarSystemModel class. Reads data from the JSON document and creates models. The order of the object creation is relevant as we need the central object before we create the orbiting objects.
